# Project Specific Data & Outputs
# We ignore the data folders to prevent uploading huge files to GitHub
data/raw/*
data/processed/*
!data/raw/.gitkeep
!data/processed/.gitkeep

# We DO NOT ignore data/external/ if it contains small important metadata like gene_list.csv
# But we ignore large files inside it just in case
data/external/*.pkl
data/external/*.nii.gz
data/external/*.vcf

